Export Manager Further processing
- ,
Date Posted: 2014/05/01 15:37:49
Ref. JB3046368
Job Description
Execute and fulfill the export annual plan.
Analyze all existing markets in the matter of market share, volume, profitability and expanding through continuous follow up and marketing contribution.
Facilitate pursuing new, international markets and design the work pattern in the new market.
Set the annual foreign sales plan and budget.
Targeted Export regions: Morocco - Algeria - Tunisia - Libya - African countries
Skills
Excellent Decision Making Skills
Strong Negotiation Skills
Highly able to Communicate Effectively and Deal with different cultures
International Trading Knowledge
Processed Poultry Marketing
